Major changed + Major additions:
- Renamed TheEntity files to appearance and screen for more clarity.
- Fixed a REALLY weird bug caused by the AI where appearance and screen files were mixed up and did not make any sense at all.
- Fixed a bug where TheEntity animation would start a few ticks late.
- Made wind only run when in battle.
- More specific with main.ts comments.
- Expanded README.md.
- Added world download.
- Fixed a bug where if a player had no teleportTickCount it would not be added and throw errors.
- Made players be teleported back to beginning of the room after TheEntity appears.
- Disabled player movements when TheEntity appears.
- Made TheEntity be teleported when the battle starts.
- Made TheEntity have an attack cooldown that spawns thunder if it will not kill the player.

